{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fund support package for NHS and social care workers and their families",
        "additional_details": "We believe by bringing in this support package, fewer families will struggle and there can be a decrease in families living in poverty. Targeted support in schools to children whose parents work in NHS and social care via additional educational support can help those children during times when their parents face extra pressure financially and at work.",
        "background": "We call on the Government to fund a support package for NHS and social care workers as the cost of living is increasing and many might facing financial struggles. This support package should include not only financial support, but support for their families including educational support for children",
